      label("second circle", (-7,0), W);
      label("first circle", (0,0), S);
      label("third circle", (2,0), E);
      label("locus of centers", (-1,1.7));
[/asy]Applying the Law of Cosines shows that the desired locus is $y^2 = -3(x-1)^2 + 16,$ as desired.
